Demarcus Devonte KIMBLE NO. 2018-KH-0925 Supreme Court of Louisiana. September 21, 2018

WRIT NOT CONSIDERED. Petitioner has not demonstrated that petitioner sought review in the court(s) below before filing in this Court nor shown the "extraordinary circumstances" that would justify *497bypassing that level of review. La.S.Ct.R. X § 5(b).
